data.description:
Step back in time and discover the unique features and nostalgic charm of this well-preserved residence. This property showcases the architectural and design trends popular in the 1970s, offering a glimpse into the past while providing a comfortable living space for modern lifestyles.
As you enter the home, open floor plan on the main level seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, providing an inviting space for gatherings and entertaining. You'll appreciate the preserved wood paneling that adorns the walls, creating a rustic ambiance and adding a touch of nostalgia.The home offers three bedrooms, each with its own character and ample natural light. Outside, the property showcases its era-appropriate curb appeal with well-maintained landscaping, a driveway with room for multiple cars. You need to add this one to your list of homes to check out!
Temp lease option is available till closing!!
